h (7) is included.</td></tr>             <tr><td>13</td><td>Minor&nbsp;7th&=
nbsp;+<br>Major&nbsp;6th/13th</td><td>Adds a major 6th/13th to a chord that=
 includes a minor 7th. May include a 9 as well (or 11, if if chord has a mi=
