         <p>A letter or icon that stands for a certain type of triad (and, =
if extended, often implies a certain type of 7th). <br>No letter or icon me=
ans a major triad <small>(or at least a major 3rd, if the 5th is raised to =
#5 or lowered to b5)</small>.</p>             <table class=3D"qualityTable"=
><tbody><tr><th>Quality</th><th>Triad Type</th><th>3rd</th><th>5th</th></tr=
>             <tr><td>m</td><td>minor</td><td>m3</td><td>5 <sup>*i.n.s.o.</=
